fficial-to-help-with-gaza-hostage-deal/0000018c-a67b-dbb4-af9f-ef7bdcbf0000</link><description>俄罗斯总统代表在莫斯科举行的一次会议上告诉以色列德鲁兹领导人，普京已经满足了内塔尼亚胡的要求，并任命副外长就此事采取行动</description><pubDate>Tue, 26 Dec 2023 14:47:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-26/ty-article/.premium/putin-appoints-senior-official-to-help-with-gaza-hostage-deal/0000018c-a67b-dbb4-af9f-ef7bdcbf0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列政界人士称，带回约旦河西岸巴勒斯坦工人不在讨论范围之内</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-26/ty-article/.premium/bringing-back-west-bank-palestinian-workers-not-on-the-table-israeli-politicians-say/0000018c-a644-db79-abee-f6e56c960000</link><description>据消息人士称，尽管安全官员认为允许巴勒斯坦工人入境将缓解西岸的紧张局势，但 10 月 7 日之后以色列公众的气氛将在未来几周内不允许这种情况发生。</description><pubDate>Tue, 26 Dec 2023 14:46:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-26/ty-article/.premium/bringing-back-west-bank-palestinian-workers-not-on-the-table-israeli-politicians-say/0000018c-a644-db79-abee-f6e56c960000</guid></item><item><title>以色列心理学家猛烈抨击卫生部“缓解”心理健康危机的计划</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-26/ty-article/.premium/israeli-psychologists-slam-health-ministry-plan-to-ease-mental-health-crisis/0000018c-a2b9-d97c-a9ec-beff7d940000</link><description>以色列卫生部希望任命不合格的“心理健康支持者”，以帮助满足预期的心理和创伤后应激障碍治疗需求激增 ■ 国家心理保健系统长期以来因忽视而受到批评</description><pubDate>Tue, 26 Dec 2023 14:42:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-26/ty-article/.premium/israeli-psychologists-slam-health-ministry-plan-to-ease-mental-health-crisis/0000018c-a2b9-d97c-a9ec-beff7d940000</guid></item><item><title>轰炸加沙历史遗迹：“以色列正在摧毁一切美丽的事物”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-26/ty-article-magazine/.premium/bombing-historical-sites-in-gaza-israel-is-destroying-everything-beautiful/0000018c-a565-df1f-a7bf-b7e53e8e0000</link><description>13 世纪的奥马里大清真寺、圣波菲里乌斯教堂、古港口的发掘现场：除了数千人死亡和数十万人流离失所外，加沙地带的数十处遗址也被以色列的轰炸摧毁</description><pu