za-fighting-on-monday/0000018c-a56f-d97c-a9ec-bfef90a20000</link><description>以色列军队宣布三名士兵死亡，其中两人在加沙死亡，一人在黎巴嫩边境附近受伤。当天晚上，军方称又有三名士兵在加沙战斗中阵亡</description><pubDate>Tue, 26 Dec 2023 09:51:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-26/ty-article/israeli-army-names-two-soldiers-killed-in-gaza-fighting-on-monday/0000018c-a56f-d97c-a9ec-bfef90a20000</guid></item><item><title>以色列MK：南美、非洲国家愿意接受来自加沙的难民，以换取付款</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-26/ty-article/israeli-mk-israel-has-received-inquiries-from-countries-to-accept-refugees-from-gaza/0000018c-a50e-d408-a99f-ed5ec4f00000</link><description>达尼·达农 (MK Dani Danon) 在接受采访时谈到巴勒斯坦人离开加沙的“自愿移民”，称这种情况“在每场战争中都会发生”。内塔尼亚胡周一表示，问题不在于让他们离开，而在于找到愿意接受他们的国家</description><pubDate>Tue, 26 Dec 2023 09:08:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-26/ty-article/israeli-mk-israel-has-received-inquiries-from-countries-to-accept-refugees-from-gaza/0000018c-a50e-d408-a99f-ed5ec4f00000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡审判的法官加快腐败案件的听证会</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-26/ty-article/.premium/judges-in-netanyahu-trial-fast-track-hearings-in-two-corruption-cases/0000018c-a2bf-d97c-a9ec-beff55100000</link><description>法官做出这一决定之前，内塔尼亚胡的律师上周要求检方推迟两起案件中关键证人的证词，因为内塔尼亚胡正忙于战争，无法与他的律师保持持续联系。</description><pubDate>Tue, 26 Dec 2023 07:27:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-26/ty-article/.premium/judges-in-netanyahu-trial-fast-track-hearings-in-two-corruption-cases/0000018c-a2bf-d97c-a9ec-beff55100000</guid></item><item><title>20,000 人死亡且仍在增加：核实加沙死亡人数的斗争</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-26/ty-article-magazine/.premium/20-000-dead-and-counting-the-battle-over-verifying-gazas-death-toll/0000018c-a0ae-d92d-addf-eaff010a0000</link><description>据哈马斯管理的卫生部称，自 10 月 7 日以来，加沙已达到 2 万人死亡的严峻里程碑。一场规模空前、强度空前的战争，谁能核实其数量？这些数字是否区分了平民和武装分子，或者空袭受害者和失控火箭弹的受害者？谁统计了加沙的死亡人数以及如何统计？</description><pubDate>Tue, 26 Dec 2023 06:44:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-26/ty-article-magazine/.premium/20-000-dead-and-counting-the-battle-over-verifying-gazas-death-toll/0000018c-a0ae-d92d-addf-eaff010a0000</guid></item></channel></rss>